import React from 'react';
import { TextField, Container, Typography } from '@material-ui/core';


function CreateReminder() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Typography variant="h4">
                Reminders
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="h6">
                Creat a reminder
            </Typography>

            <form 
            noValidate 
            >
                <TextField 
                label="Reminder"
                variant="outlined"
                color="secondary"
                />
            </form>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default CreateReminder
